 false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 630996, "username": "punish19", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/punish19", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/55bf/324c/630996_mini.png?m=1728444060", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/55bf/324c/630996_normal.png?m=1728444060", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/55bf/324c/630996_large.png?m=1728444060", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/55bf/324c/630996_xlarge.png?m=1728444060", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/55bf/324c/630996_xlarge.png?m=1728444060", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/55bf/324c/630996_xlarge.png?m=1728444060", "created": 1685041611, "last_modified": 1728444060}, "last_reply_by": "mokiki", "last_touched": 1728853684, "title": "最近好多蟑螂，有大也有小，求治、驱赶蟑螂的法子", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1079764", "created": 1728785432, "deleted": 0, "content": "家里也就养了猫，以前偶尔一只、两只大的那种，我家的猫还会去追去抓的，所以家里几乎没蟑螂。\r\n今年入秋后多了好多，不但有大的，还有那种防不胜防的小的，买了那种诱捕盒子，但效果甚微，几乎没有。\r\n现在只能晚上关了厨房，洗手间门，不让猫进去，然后在里面摆上蟑螂药，早上起床再收起来。\r\n开始的时候有点效果的，但后来也失效了。\r\n请教各位有什么实用的方法吗？", "content_rendered": "家里也就养了猫，以前偶尔一只、两只大的那种，我家的猫还会去追去抓的，所以家里几乎没蟑螂。<br />今年入秋后多了好多，不但有大的，还有那种防不胜防的小的，买了那种诱捕盒子，但效果甚微，几乎没有。<br />现在只能晚上关了厨房，洗手间门，不让猫进去，然后在里面摆上蟑螂药，早上起床再收起来。<br />开始的时候有点效果的，但后来也失效了。<br />请教各位有什么实用的方法吗？", "last_modified": 1728795836, "replies": 52, "id": 1079764}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1670319927", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1670319927", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 4058, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1670319927", "stars": 1283, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name"